      },
      {
        id: 'governing-law',
        title: '6. Governing Law & Updates',
        content: 'These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction in which we operate, without regard to conflict of law principles. We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time by updating this page.'
      }
